What is it?
===========

The thunar-diff-plugin is a plugin for the Thunar File Manager, which
adds "select for compare" operations to the file context menus. Using this plugin you
will be able to configure a good compare application to Thunar.


Required packages
=================

thunar-diff-plugin depends on the following packages:

 - Thunar 1.2.0 or above

Supported compare application
==========================

thunar-diff-plugin supports many compare application. For example: beyondcompare/kdiff/diffmerge.


Installation
============

The file 'INSTALL' contains generic installation instructions. 

How to report bugs?
===================

Bugs should be reported to my email address(eagle_xmw@aliyun.com). 
